			<p>(1) R. <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-005042">Ministry of Foreign Affairs</orgName>, <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/3169070/rome.html">Rome</placeName></p>
			<p>(2) R. Representation of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3175395/italian-republic.html">Italy</placeName> for <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/390903/hellenic-republic.html">Greece</placeName>, <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/264371/athens.html">Athens</placeName></p>
			<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/734077/thessaloniki.html">Thessaloniki</placeName>, <date when="1943-08-11">11th August
					[1943]</date></p>
			<p>1) End of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-872" type="subject">Jewish colony</term> of <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/734077/thessaloniki.html">Thessaloniki</placeName></p>
			<p>2) Follow-up to the cable of this R. Office no. 4050/889 of 11th inst.</p>
			<p>The last <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> still remaining in the
					<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2382" type="camp">“Baron Hirsch” Ghetto</placeName> have left
				in the night from <date when="1943-08-10">10th</date> to <date when="1943-08-11">11th August</date>.</p>
			<p>The special <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-429">SS Police</orgName> left yesterday. Their chief
					<persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000429">Vesleceny</persName> [sic] left this morning by
				aeroplane for <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2950159/berlin.html">Berlin</placeName>.</p>
			<p>The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewish</term> colony of <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/734077/thessaloniki.html">Thessaloniki</placeName>, which was founded before the discovery of America
				and which comprised approx. 60,000 people, is no more. Over the centuries the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> had set up highly valuable <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-889" type="subject">factories</term>, such as that of the <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/3175395/italian-republic.html">Italian</placeName>
				<term ref="#ehri_dr_torres" type="subject">Torres</term>, to name but one, which produced fabrics and jute and was the most important
				in the entire <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/685608/balkan-peninsula.html">Balkans</placeName>.</p>
			<p>They had amassed enormous <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-888" type="subject">wealth</term>, which was
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-660" type="subject">plundered and stolen</term> by the <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/390903/hellenic-republic.html">Greeks</placeName> and by the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1152?dlid=deu" type="subject">Germans</term>.</p>
			<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-529" type="subject">The elimination</term> of the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Israelite</term> colony took place and was completed
				among <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-345" type="subject">atrocities, horrors and crimes</term> such as
				I had never heard described in the history of all times and of all peoples.</p>
			<p>The <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3175395/italian-republic.html">Italian</placeName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Israelite</term> colony was able to reach safety by
				moving to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/264371/athens.html">Athens</placeName>; the same can be said of the small <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/3865483/argentine-republic.html">Argentine</placeName> and <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2264397/portuguese-republic.html">Portuguese</placeName> colonies.</p>
			<p>The <ref target="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/jc-places-place-jmp-685">Spanish</ref> colony, which for the past two months
				had lived in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-520" type="subject">hope of being transferred to
					Spain</term>, at the last moment received a Spanish refusal and was <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deported</term> by the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1032" type="subject">Germans</term>, including the Spanish Vice-Consul,
				who had been accepted and acknowledged as such and had served Spain in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/734077/thessaloniki.html">Thessaloniki</placeName> for a great many years.</p>
			<p>For us <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3175395/italian-republic.html">Italians</placeName> the elimination of our <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewish</term> colony means an extremely serious loss
				that cannot be measured in millions. Suffice it to say that before the present war the <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/3175395/italian-republic.html">Italian</placeName> merchant marine was the second in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/734077/thessaloniki.html">Thessaloniki</placeName>, immediately after the <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/390903/hellenic-republic.html">Greek</placeName>. The maritime traffic was mostly originated by the
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-933" type="subject">trade</term> and by the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-890" type="subject">factories of the Italian Jews</term> of <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/734077/thessaloniki.html">Thessaloniki</placeName>.</p>
			<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_giuseppe_catruccio">G. Castruccio</persName></p>
